      "settings": {
        "delivery": "<p>Our standard lead time for all items is approx 8 to 12 weeks (May be longer for Devon, Cornwall, Wales & Scotland), need it sooner? <a href=\"https://www.eatsleeplive.co.uk/pages/get-in-touch\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.eatsleeplive.co.uk/pages/get-in-touch\">get in touch</a> to see how we can help, we can do miracles occasionally!</p><p>We aim to deliver all of our furniture via our craftsmen that made your items.</p><p>We do occasionally deliver via our trusted couriers when needed.</p><p><br/>We will contact you with as much notice as possible (usually 7-14 days before) to book your delivery. <br/><br/><strong>Moving house or have renovations?<br/></strong><br/>Order now to get the ball rolling and we will work with you on timescales. Project or move  delayed? Don't worry we can hold your furniture until you are ready and then deliver as soon as possible after completion! <br/><br/>Any questions contact us on </p><p>tel: <strong>01159 700 060<br/></strong>email: <strong>info@eatsleeplive.co.uk<br/></strong><a href=\"https://direct.lc.chat/4777881/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"live chat\"><strong><br/></strong></a><strong>*We deliver to mainland UK only.</strong></p><p><strong>For Cornwall, Wales & Scotland. Please call us to discuss before ordering as there may be delivery charges.</strong></p>",
        "fully_assembled": "<p>Most of our pieces will arrive fully assembled and some will need to be assembled, such as dining tables, beds and desks.</p><p>Our assembly service is included free of charge if delivered by our own craftsmen. </p><p>Occasionally we may need to deliver via a trusted courier who may not offer this service, however we can give clear instructions, don't worry its all very simple and easy! <br/><br/><em><strong>PLEASE NOTE:</strong></em><em> We can not be held responsible for furniture not fitting in your house or being able to get it in your room of choice, please check dimensions and accessibility before ordering.</em></p><p><em>We do not hang mirrors or install your TV equipment etc, our service is to simply deliver your Eat Sleep Live items to your home.</em></p><p></p><p><em><strong>Returns & Refunds Policy - easy no hassle </strong></em><a href=\"/pages/returns-and-refunds-policy\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Returns And Refunds Policy\"><em><strong>learn more</strong></em></a></p><p> </p>",
        "assembly_required": ""
      }
    },
