      "settings": {
        "subtitle": "PAY, YOUR WAY.",
        "title": "Kit out your home with our flexible payment options",
        "description": "<p><strong>ONLINE ORDERS:</strong></p><p><strong>Pay in full via debit/credit card</strong> - Visa, Mastercard, Maestro, Amex or Paypal</p><p> </p><p><strong>OFFLINE ORDERS: (via phone, email or in-store)</strong></p><p><strong>Pay in 2 - </strong>25% or 50% deposit on placing order</p><p>Balance paid on booking delivery</p><p></p><p><strong>Pay in 3 </strong>- 1/3 deposit on placing order</p><p> 1/3 halfway during lead time</p><p> balance paid on booking delivery</p><p>to arrange one of our payment plans please <a href=\"https://www.eatsleeplive.co.uk/pages/get-in-touch\" title=\"get in touch\">get in touch</a></p><p> </p><p><strong>BACS PAYMENTS:</strong></p><p>Not a problem we can give you the details once you enquire/order<br/><br/></p><p></p><p><strong>RETURNS & REFUND POLICY - </strong><em><strong>easy no hassle </strong></em><a href=\"/pages/returns-and-refunds-policy\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Returns And Refunds Policy\"><em><strong>learn more<br/><br/></strong></em></a></p><p></p><p><strong>QUESTIONS?</strong></p><p><strong>We are always happy to help</strong></p><p><strong>tel: 01159 700 060</strong></p><p><strong>email: info@eatsleeplive.co.uk</strong></p><p><strong> or </strong><a href=\"https://www.eatsleeplive.co.uk/pages/get-in-touch#visit-our-workshop\"><strong>visit us. </strong></a></p><p> *Terms & conditions apply.</p>"
